<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8" standalone="no"?><?Xpress productLine="ncc-clause" ?><clause id="_51b16f6c-8397-4cb6-a2c5-d216f78750b6" outputclass="ncc-clause"><meta><facet building="Class 1b"/><facet building="Class 10a"/><facet building="Class 10b"/><facet building="Class 10c"/><facet building="Class 1a"/></meta><sptc>E3D3</sptc><title id="_b90500b3-41cf-4825-abb5-805589646f78">Stretcher facility in lifts</title><archive-num>2019: E3.2</archive-num><subclause id="_3fc28da7-eb1c-4e3d-bda6-bb434a4fe071" outputclass="subclause"><title id="_7fc07e9b-27b0-4f1d-9014-f1484efc73cc">SubClause</title><num>1</num><p>A stretcher facility in accordance with (2) must be providedâ€”</p><ol outputclass="alpha"><li id="_de4488fb-4243-4082-b8c1-02738bbf4b37">in at least one emergency lift <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/5e2c1f63-e589-4ce1-95e8-5c3e286a7aff/1432_4.0.0.xml#_af6fde9f-147d-4782-8b85-42044e80fd42" id="_182e4745-96ff-4a59-8b3e-1b88da28b4ed" scope="local" type="abcb-glossentry">required</xref> by <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/5e2c1f63-e589-4ce1-95e8-5c3e286a7aff/2785_2.11.0.xml#_24b809f8-d1bf-4b8b-85bf-270131c517c9" id="_5bc036de-c22a-416d-bbe8-cd2c99020dff" scope="local" type="clause">E3D5</xref>; or</li><li id="_7292127c-c591-4820-bef8-1157c3486cfb">where an emergency lift is not <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/5e2c1f63-e589-4ce1-95e8-5c3e286a7aff/1432_4.0.0.xml#_af6fde9f-147d-4782-8b85-42044e80fd42" id="_7ee2dd85-b152-4fa3-853e-adcfb583f1da" scope="local" type="abcb-glossentry">required</xref>, if passenger lifts are installed to serve any storey above an <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/5e2c1f63-e589-4ce1-95e8-5c3e286a7aff/1252_2.0.0.xml#_cd986c21-bc64-43a9-954d-86e35d335b74" id="_2a98c15c-7e33-4fd0-80c8-d1f4e589eb8d" scope="local" type="abcb-glossentry">effective height</xref> of 12 m, in at least one of those lifts to serve each floor served by the lifts.</li></ol></subclause><subclause id="_176855df-4bf6-42f2-b4d4-3f2d3b606836" outputclass="subclause"><title id="_d8799c1c-c74d-4b62-bb62-3375cd6858b8">SubClause</title><num>2</num><p>A stretcher facility must accommodate a raised stretcher with a patient lying on it horizontally by providing a clear space not less than 600 mm wide x 2000 mm long x 1400 mm high above the floor level.</p></subclause></clause>